com.tomtom.cpp.select

Class DeltaPartitionerPredicate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomtom.cpp.select.DeltaPartitionerPredicate

  • public class DeltaPartitionerPredicate
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements partitioning for delta. In order to download a large delta, partitioning needs to be performed, which is done based on the size of the delta. The first partitioning estimates are made based on the full delta size without filtering. Note that the delta size is related to the number of modified features only. The default partition size is 4096 (feature modifications). For specific use cases, filtering based on the estimated feature count is not enough. A more precise sampling can be done by providing any number of withPreciseSizeSampler sub-predicates.
